   <text:p text:style-name="Standard" loext:marker-style-name="T5"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Here we have a question with an image and text, and the answers are in words.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P19" loext:marker-style-name="T5"><text:span text:style-name="T5">In </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T15">Scripture </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">App Builder, you need to put the image (a JPG or PNG file) in the </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T26">Illustrations </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">tab for the quiz book.</text:span></text:p>
